<h1 class="jazz-page-title">Form Field</h1>

<p>
A Form Field is a composite form construct that encapsulates a form input along with its corresponding label, required/optional indicator, field-specific assistive content, and field-specific error messages.
</p>

{{ example("/components/form-field/form-field-example-simple", "Demonstration", "code-panel-form-field") }}

<h2>Best Practices</h2>

<ul>

    <li>Clearly label each form input.</li>
    <li>Provide field-specific assistive content to clarify how the field should be used/completed.</li>
    <li>Clearly label fields as required/optional.  If most of the fields are required, indicate which are optional.  If most of the fields are optional, indicate which are required.</li>
    <li>Capitalize the first word of the label and any proper names as they would normally be capitalized.</li>
</ul>

