<h2>Detailed Specification</h2>

<h3>Design</h3>

<ul>
    <li>A Form Field is composed of the label, the input control and the error message component.</li>
    <li>The input control contained within the form field tags can be any simple form control.</li>
    <li>The form field is designed to contain only one input control at a time.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Code</h3>

<ul>
    <li>The label and the input tags are wrapped by a div with the <span class="code">jazz-form-field</span> style.</li>
    <li>The input tag should have the <span class="code">jazz-input</span> class in order to be styled properly.</li>
    <li>In order to show that the field is required the label needs to have the <span class="code">required</span> attribute set to show the red asterisk next to the label.</li>
        {% highlight "html" %}
           <label for="my-input" required>Text Field 1</label>
        {% endhighlight %}
    <li>In order to override or specify messages for validation errors you can add a span/s with the role = alert and the class <span class="jazz-form-field-error-msg"></span>.
          {% highlight "html" %}
              <span role="alert" class="jazz-form-field-error-msg">'Field 1' is required.</span>
          {% endhighlight %}
    </li>
    <li>The input control needs to have the <span class="code">jazz-input</span> class so that the styles for the input component are applied as designed.
        {% highlight "html" %}
           <div class="jazz-form-field">
               <label for="my-input" required>Text Field 1</label>
               <input class="jazz-input" id="my-input" type="text" placeholder="Placeholder" />
           </div>
        {% endhighlight %}
    </li>
    <li>To show error messages you can add a span with the class jazz-form-field-error-msg below the input control
        {% highlight "html" %}
            <div class="jazz-form-field">
               <label for="my-input" required>Text Field 1</label>
               <input class="jazz-input" id="my-input" type="text" placeholder="Placeholder" />
               <span role="alert" class="jazz-form-field-error-msg">'Field 1' is required.</span>
            </div>
        {% endhighlight %}
    </li>
</ul>

